$trip2g_user_space $mol_view
	sub /
		\Profile...
		<= Open $mol_button_major
			click <= open null
		<= Dialog $mol_view
			dom_name \dialog
			attr * open <= open_status null null|string
			sub /
				\Content...
				<= Email $mol_view
					sub / <= user_email \
				<= Close $mol_button_minor
					click <= close null
